[{"tag_name":"0.1.0","name":"Initial Relase","body":"It Works!\r\n\r\nA simple Tesla Overlay to request atmosphere to reload the `hosts` file, and to toggle on/off hosts file entries.  It will read all files in the `/atmoshere/hosts/` directory.\r\n\r\nAll lines starting with `#` are treated as section Headers.\r\n\r\nIf the line starts with a digit, it is expected to be an IP address and toggleable.\r\n\r\nToggling is performed by prepending or removing a `;`.\r\n\r\nAll other lines are simply ignored.\r\n\r\nHosts files are reloaded in DNS MITM each time the overlay is hidden.\r\n\r\nSimply install by unzipping and placing the `.ovl` in `/switch/.overlays/`.","assets":[{"size":333248,"browser_download_url":"https://github.com/znxDomain/DNS-MITM_Manager/releases/download/0.1.0/DNS-MITM_Manager.ovl.zip"}]}]